you can pass multiple middleware using array

const middleware1 = (req, res, next) => {
    // code here
    next();
}
const middleware2 = (req, res, next) => {
    // code here
    next();
}

app.use([middleware1, middleware2]);



-----------------------------------------

specify middleware to be applied to some routes or a route using:
    app.use('/route that starts with:...', middlewareName)
        like ->  app.use('/api', middlewareName);


