when you call next(erro) that is, you pass an arg to the next func(), 
the express authomaticaly thinks that something went wrong and it 
will automatically skip the execution of the request to the error 
handuller function i.e app.use((err, req, res, next) => {...}) skipping
the next middleware and the route handuller. 